# Caddy on the game host: terminates TLS for the CloudFront origin hostname
# (the box's own A record) with an automatic ACME cert, and reverse-proxies
# the whitelist bot's routes to the bot on localhost:3000. CloudFront
# (hamaro.rowan.wang) is the only intended client; the bot additionally
# checks the X-Origin-Verify header CloudFront adds (ORIGIN_VERIFY_SECRET).
mc.rowan.wang {
	reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:3000
}
